{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Preheat oven to 170°C.","Place chocolate in mixing bowl and grate <b>6 sec\/speed 8<b>. Transfer to a bowl and set aside. Clean mixing bowl.","Place eggs, sugar and milk in mixing bowl then mix <b>3 min\/37°C\/speed 3<b>. Generously dredge the base of a 1.5 litre oven-proof dish with 20 g cocoa then lay in half the brioche pieces. Dredge again with 20 g cocoa and scatter with grated chocolate and raisins. Top with a second layer of brioche.","Pour the egg mixture in so the oven-proof dish is half full, then allow it to stand 5 minutes for brioche to absorb the liquid, then top with remaining mixture. Sprinkle with remaining 10 g cocoa and extra sugar.","Bake for 50–60 minutes (170°C) until pudding is puffy and set in the centre. Allow pudding to settle and cool slightly before serving with cream."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["200 g dark chocolate, in small pieces or callets","6 medium eggs","160 g sugar, plus extra for garnish","700 g whole milk","50 g cocoa powder","8 slices brioche, day old, halved","50 g raisins","cream, to serve"]}],"id":"r238748","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-HuWTGw8w8b8\/XZWclByPadI\/AAAAAAAAebs\/1_2W0w8znN4rzpaijbEqfzLyD7OQtyuUACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_21gziJzC0PxmsJKa.png","title":"Chocolate Bread 'N Butter Pudding","publishedAt":"2018-02-19T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"13 g","fat":"17 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"68 g","calories":"1862 kJ \/ 445 kcal"},"usefulItems":"large oven-proof dish or roasting tray (approx. 30 cm), oven","hintsAndTricks":["Use chocolate with at least 70% cocoa for the best result.","If you cannot get brioche, you can use thick-cut white bread.","For an alcoholic twist, macerate the raisins in dark rum before adding in step 5."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h 25m","8 portions"]}